关联规则基础

关联规则是用来表示项集之间的关联或者相关的规则。一个关联规则有以下形式： \[ A\Rightarrow B \] 其中 \(A,B\) 是不相交的项集。 有3种应用最广泛的用来选择规则的度量。
1. support: the percentage of cases in the data that contains both \(A\) and \(B\)
2. confidence: the percentage of cases containing \(A\) that also contain \(B\)
3. lift: the ratio of confidence to the percentage of cases containing \(B\)

3者的计算公式如下： \[ support(A\Rightarrow B) = P(A\cap B) \\ confidence(A\Rightarrow B) = P(B|A) = \frac{P(AB)}{P(A)} \\ lift(A\Rightarrow B) = \frac{confidence(A\Rightarrow B)}{P(B)} = \frac{P(AB)}{P(A)P(B)} \]

关联规则挖掘

一个经典的关联规则挖掘算法是 APRIORI，它是一个逐层、广度优先算法，计数频繁出现的项集，然后从中找出关联规则

library(arules)
rules.all <- apriori(titanic.raw)

rules <- apriori(titanic.raw, control = list(verbose = F),
                 parameter = list(minlen = 2, supp = 0.005, conf = 0.8),
                 appearance = list(rhs = c("Survived=No", "Survived=Yes"), default = "lhs"))
quality(rules) <- round(quality(rules), digits=3)
rules.sorted <- sort(rules, by="lift")
inspect(rules.sorted)

移除冗余

上例中的 rules.sorted 中，rule1 涵盖了 rule2（成为 super），rule1 已经告诉我们所有存活下来的儿童。再有4，7，8相对于3，6，5是冗余的。我们使用以下代码来去掉冗余的规则。

subset.matrix <- is.subset(rules.sorted, rules.sorted)
subset.matrix[lower.tri(subset.matrix, diag = T)] <- NA
#inspect(subset.matrix)
redundant <- colSums(subset.matrix, na.rm = T) >= 1
which(redundant)
##  {Class=2nd,Sex=Female,Age=Child,Survived=Yes} 
##                                              2 
##  {Class=1st,Sex=Female,Age=Adult,Survived=Yes} 
##                                              4 
## {Class=Crew,Sex=Female,Age=Adult,Survived=Yes} 
##                                              7 
##  {Class=2nd,Sex=Female,Age=Adult,Survived=Yes} 
##                                              8
rules.pruned <- rules.sorted[!redundant]
inspect(rules.pruned)
##    lhs                               rhs            support confidence
## 1  {Class=2nd,Age=Child}          => {Survived=Yes} 0.011   1.000     
## 4  {Class=1st,Sex=Female}         => {Survived=Yes} 0.064   0.972     
## 2  {Class=2nd,Sex=Female}         => {Survived=Yes} 0.042   0.877     
## 5  {Class=Crew,Sex=Female}        => {Survived=Yes} 0.009   0.870     
## 9  {Class=2nd,Sex=Male,Age=Adult} => {Survived=No}  0.070   0.917

理解规则

在 rules.pruned 列表中的第一条规则： {Class=2nd,Age=Child} => {Survived=Yes} 仅仅表示 class 2nd 的儿童都存活了，但并不能说明 class 2nd 的儿童比其它 class 的儿童有更高的存活率。为了进行验证我们使用如下代码：

rules2 <- apriori(titanic.raw, 
                 parameter = list(minlen = 3, supp = 0.002, conf = 0.2),
                 appearance = list(rhs = c("Survived=Yes"),
                                   lhs = c("Class=1st", "Class=2nd", "Class=3rd", "Age=Child", "Age=Adult"),
                                   default = "none"))
## Apriori
## 
## Parameter specification:
##  confidence minval smax arem  aval originalSupport support minlen maxlen
##         0.2    0.1    1 none FALSE            TRUE   0.002      3     10
##  target   ext
##   rules FALSE
## 
## Algorithmic control:
##  filter tree heap memopt load sort verbose
##     0.1 TRUE TRUE  FALSE TRUE    2    TRUE
## 
## Absolute minimum support count: 4 
## 
## set item appearances ...[6 item(s)] done [0.00s].
## set transactions ...[6 item(s), 2201 transaction(s)] done [0.00s].
## sorting and recoding items ... [6 item(s)] done [0.00s].
## creating transaction tree ... done [0.00s].
## checking subsets of size 1 2 3 done [0.00s].
## writing ... [6 rule(s)] done [0.00s].
## creating S4 object  ... done [0.00s].
rules.sorted2 <- sort(rules2, by="confidence")
inspect(rules.sorted2)
##   lhs                      rhs            support     confidence lift     
## 1 {Class=2nd,Age=Child} => {Survived=Yes} 0.010904134 1.0000000  3.0956399
## 2 {Class=1st,Age=Child} => {Survived=Yes} 0.002726034 1.0000000  3.0956399
## 5 {Class=1st,Age=Adult} => {Survived=Yes} 0.089504771 0.6175549  1.9117275
## 4 {Class=2nd,Age=Adult} => {Survived=Yes} 0.042707860 0.3601533  1.1149048
## 3 {Class=3rd,Age=Child} => {Survived=Yes} 0.012267151 0.3417722  1.0580035
## 6 {Class=3rd,Age=Adult} => {Survived=Yes} 0.068605179 0.2408293  0.7455209

以上结果表明 class 1st 和 class 2nd 有相同的存活率。之所以 class 1st 没有出现在一次结果中，是因为被 supp 给限制了。
